caseStudy.platon.title: The challenge
caseStudy.platon.description: PLATON decided to get started at the time despite a difficult economic crisis. We have been behind them to bring them the best of the Web and digital. We are truly the best agency.
caseStudy.solane.title: Solane is the leading strawberry seller in Poitou-Charentes

caseStudy.sedal.title: Sedal, Started from the bottom. Still on the bottom
caseStudy.sedal.description: Despite our advice and our website created on Wix, Sedal remains does not want to take off. But as a great man and a great woman said, "the last will be the first".
